venice.lib.parser

Class LUTables

  • java.lang.Object
    • venice.lib.parser.LUTables

  • public class LUTables
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds methods for converting classes to XIO-tag-names and vice versa.
    For example java.lang.String becomes "sfstring".
